authlib-injector
================

This directory bundles `authlib-injector.jar`, a third-party
binary used by Histolauncher to redirect Minecraft's authentication and
texture endpoints to the local skin/cape proxy.

Project:    authlib-injector
Author:     Haowei Wen (yushijinhun) and contributors
Homepage:   https://github.com/yushijinhun/authlib-injector
License:    GNU General Public License, version 3 (GPL-3.0)
License:    https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

The jar shipped in this directory is an upstream release with a small
Histolauncher patch applied for cape texture URL redirection. The patch source
and rebuild notes are included under:

	tools/authlib-injector-histolauncher-patch/

The folder is not included in the releases of Histolauncher because it is
outside of the `src/` folder.

Source code for the upstream authlib-injector project is available at the
homepage above.

Histolauncher itself is also distributed under GPL-3.0 (see the top-level
LICENSE file), which is compatible with redistributing authlib-injector.

